
<div style={{ textAlign: "center", marginTop: "50px" }}>

You expected the entire page to be centered

But inline style only centers the content inside the div, not the whole page.

Example:

<div style={{ textAlign: "center" }}>


This centers only the text, not the whole page.

If you want the div itself centered, you must use:

<div style={{
  marginTop: "50px",
  display: "flex",
  flexDirection: "column",
  alignItems: "center",
}}>